{"tid":1709681,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【恥笑，TVB已經阻止唔到我哋】每日洗版任務 - Skin Biotics","createTime":"2019-11-12T03:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T23:10:12.000Z","uid":267969,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"bf0b20371469ac311ddbabcca03cbe11758c2845","tid":1709681,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:00:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">恥笑，TVB真係驚無廣告到仆街</span></strong></span><br />\n話我哋TG logo侵權，要求TG暫停我哋channel，<br />\n但就算channel停賽，維多C依然收到超過<span style=\"color: red;\">1092</span>個嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIdeas are bulletproof，你有種就搞掂埋連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw, TG channel 剛剛已經解封<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>既然TVB咁驚洗版<br />\n我哋唔好俾佢停，好唔好？</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【抵制CCTVB 每日任務】</span></strong><br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <br />\n <br />\n是日精選@12 Nov 2019 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Skin Biotics</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/skinBIOTICShk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FskinBIOTICShk%2F&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYn8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=a21f8c6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/skinBIOTICShk/</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>※記得用留言template</strong></span></span><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留言重點</span></strong>係全力阻止廣告商簽訂下年合約</strong> <br />\n<blockquote>無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z7F2Ltu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz7F2Ltu.jpg&h=75cd3cbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>講下臭屎</strong></span><br />\n唔止落TVB廣告，仲要贊助TVB旅遊節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n產品功效亂9咁吹，真係無眼睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1️⃣「含冰河幹細胞萃取物」<br />\n一棵菜都有幹細胞啦 ，so what <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2️⃣「補充水分，滲透至肌膚底層」<br />\n開水喉洗面，都可以滲透底層啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又可以用呢幅圖留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jVMxofQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjVMxofQ.jpg&h=de0f58e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SS8qitc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSS8qitc.jpg&h=49c4d6d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得bookmark</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: TVB廣告客戶名單！！</strong></span> <br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYn8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=42dd6254\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a>  <br />\n －－－－－－－ <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">請即follow:</span></strong> <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYn8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=3104079b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb <br />\nTG 綜合狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYn8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=757ce1df\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 抵制綜合組: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2cctvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2cctvb&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYn8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=028010cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2cctvb</a><br />\nTG CCTVB記者實時位置狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/nomoretvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnomoretvb&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYn8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=2507d64c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nomoretvb</a>"},{"pid":"50cb998a1c794094819a5d1c52c6588df058c641","tid":1709681,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48639ecc83cd30a8345f2ae615d4399d7a38f425","tid":1709681,"uid":56444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:01:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0b15dffc9ef95f80b2ba4ba07a5db27c70ff285","tid":1709681,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:01:48.000Z","msg":"組織工會 全面罷工"},{"pid":"85a9e01ccbe838d6a12be97bbed21390db81c6e1","tid":1709681,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim